\pard{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf2\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li360\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj An author can see all the papers they have personally submitted.\par
