{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}An author can see the status (pending/accepted/rejected) of any paper they have personally submitted.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}An author can see the status of any paper in which they are labeled as an author.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}An author can see the paper details of any paper they have personally submitted.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}An author can see the paper details of any paper in which they are labeled as an author.\par
{\pntext\f2\'B7\tab}An author can upload the camera-ready copy of a paper.\par
